short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Yours Magic Dressup Games is an innovative extension combining web images with your photos for a magical, darling dress-up effect!
short.zh_CN: 换装大师是一款创新的浏览器插件，允许用户轻松地将网页上的图片与自己的照片进行组合，实现虚拟换装的效果

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: DressUp Master is an innovative browser extension that allows users to effortlessly combine images from web pages with their own photos to achieve a virtual dress-up effect. Whether you want to try on the latest fashion outfits or replace clothes in your photos, this plugin has got you covered. With simple drag-and-drop operations and intelligent image recognition, the dress-up experience has never been more convenient and fun. Experience DressUp Master now and explore endless possibilities!
